{"search_data": "Himachal PradeshNai Raahein Nai Manzilien Scheme in HP to Identify Unexplored Tourist PlacesHimachal Pradesh Nai Raahein Nai Manzilien Scheme CircuitsTourism Dept. has prepared 9 circuits under Nai Rahen Nai Manzil Scheme 2018. The names of these 9 circuits are as follows:-Jogindernagar-Barot-Kothi Kohar-Rajgungja-Bir-BillingSundernagar-Chail Chowk-Kamru Nag-Shikari Devi-JanjheliShimla-Khara Pathar-Rohru-Sandasu-Larot-Chanshal-Dodra KwarDhauladhar CircuitBuddhist CircuitBhakra-Bilaspur-Sundernagar-Jogindernagar-Pong DamSolan-Habban-Rajgarh-ShillaiManali-Rohtan-Tandi-Udaipur-KillarNarkanda-Baghi-Khadrala-Chini (Kalpa)-Pangi CircuitA committee of Tourism, PWD, Forests, Language, Art and Culture Officers will make a visit to the selected circuits. This committee will propose the activities which needs to be carried out in these circuits after consulting the local panchayats and other stakeholders.Works / Activities \u2013 HP Nai Rahen Nai Manzil SchemeHP govt. will carry out various developmental activities in these unexplored and untapped tourist places to diversify tourism. Infrastructure development and other facilities will be the primary focus. These activities are as follows:-ParksToiletsRain SheltersStreet PathsSolid Waste ImprovementWalking TrailsBeautification of TemplesLandscapingSaraisCommunity HallsTrekkers HostelRoads WideningSignals & Traffic DirectionsParkingsLighting & DustbinsThe state govt. will encourage Home Stays through private parties, Nature Walks, Eco-Trails, Treks, Hikes, Trips to Orchards etc.He said that this would also generate employment opportunities by way of promotion of local cuisines, Folk artist, Local Artisans, Tour Guides, Eco-Guides, Adventure Guides etc.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}